# Step 2: Persona (System Prompt)
# VHS Configuration

Output "02-role-and-persona.gif"

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 650
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Start demo
Type "python3 demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Question: swap program (same as all other steps)
Type "swap program"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Exit
Type "exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
